				<button type="button" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-4 py-2 bg-indigo-600 border border-transparent text-white rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 font-semibold transition-colors shadow-sm" id="btnSubmitDuplicate">Dupliquer</button>
